seo: Flink,漏洞检测,CVE-2020-17519,任意文件读取,高危漏洞
summary: 该插件用于检测Flink-jobmanager是否存在CVE-2020-17519任意文件读取漏洞，通过构造特定请求判断目标系统是否受影响。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Flink-jobmanager has the CVE-2020-17519 arbitrary file read vulnerability. It determines if the target system is affected by constructing specific requests.
